Minister of Transport, Rotimi Amaechi, has revealed he doesn’t believe in the Nigeria Police.
Amaechi made this known in the part 7 of his leaked tape as shared by Reno Omokri. Reno Omokri captioned it: “WATCH and SHARE: In #AmaechiTapes part 7, Rotimi @ChibuikeAmaechi reveals he does not believe in the Nigerian Police. He says they are corrupt and can be induced with money. Yet @OfficialAPCNg expect @PoliceNG to help them rig out @OfficialPDPNig.